{
  "stem": "22840.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The place had no-- it was in the valley.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It has no strategic value.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "There was no garrison there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So over the night, it was under the control of the partisans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And over the day, they would retreat or-- or walk around until their scouts have seen a German patrol.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They will retreat to the mountains.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was kind of a semi no man land, going between the hands, terrorized by both the partisans and the Germans.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Robbed by both of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one day, some partisan decided to sleep in the hut that I was in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was log hut, and it had a basement where potatoes were kept, and there was a place beneath the-- beneath the roof.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The partisan came and slept beneath the roof-- and it was warm there because the chimney-- and left.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A week later, two weeks, some time later, the Germans came and looked for partisans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they searched every single house, one after another.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they found-- I don't know how you call it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I know the Hebrew name, [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's a piece of metal, in which you put cartridges.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In the Mauser type guns that the German used, you would put in a protrusion and push it in, so you could put five cartridges in a gun very quickly, and load the gun very quickly.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And all the ammunition come with these little pieces of metal, the cartridges were pushed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They found one of these with five cartridges-- the Germans-- in the upper part.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Jozef was taken for interrogation up the mountain, to the other village, which is on top of the mountain.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
